AdvanceMAME with rapid fire function.

AdvanceMAMEにシンクロ連射機能を追加しました。
メニューに追加された "Rapid Fire" より、ボタンごとに連射有無と間隔を設定できます。
さらに、ボタンの追加が可能となっています。
ショットボタンに連射なし、ありの2つを用意できるので、連射ありだけではうまくプレイできないゲームにも対応できます。


This version of AdvanceMAME has been added with a rapid fire function.
You can select "Rapid Fire" from config menu to enable rapid fire and select the rapid interval for each button.
In addition, buttons can be added.
For example, you can add an extra shot button with rapid fire function to play with normal (no rapid fire) button and rapid fire button.



AdvanceMAME/MESS emulators and AdvanceMENU frontend
===================================================

AdvanceMAME/MESS are unofficial MAME/MESS versions with an
advanced video support for helping the use with TVs, Arcade
monitors, PC monitors and LCD screens.

AdvanceMENU is a frontend for the AdvanceMAME, AdvanceMESS, MAME,
MESS and any other emulator.

They run in Linux, Mac OS X, DOS, Windows and in all the other
platforms supported by the SDL library.

The official site of AdvanceMAME/MESS is :

    http://www.advancemame.it/

